ots</span><span>Kid-friendly crunch</span></div></div><section class="section" id="our-story"><div class="container story-grid"><div class="story-photo reveal"><img src="/images/lifestyle/fish-cheese.webp" alt="The Munching Queen Fish and Cheese snacks styled for sharing" width="1080" height="1350" loading="lazy"></div><div class="story-card reveal"><span class="eyebrow" data-en="Our story" data-id="Cerita kami">Our story</span><h2 data-en="A family kitchen with a bigger dream." data-id="Dapur keluarga dengan mimpi yang lebih besar.">A family kitchen with a bigger dream.</h2><p data-en="We are parents and snack enthusiasts from Surabaya. In 2016, we introduced Kroepoek Waroeng at a food expo in Dubai. Seeing international guests light up over Indonesian crackers gave us a mission: share our food heritage in a ready-to-munch, joyfully flavoured way." data-id="Kami adalah para orang tua dan pencinta camilan dari Surabaya. Pada 2016, kami memperkenalkan Kroepoek Waroeng di pameran makanan Dubai. Antusiasme pengunjung internasional terhadap kerupuk Indonesia memberi kami misi: membagikan warisan kuliner ini dalam bentuk siap santap yang penuh rasa.">We are parents and snack enthusiasts from Surabaya. In 2016, we introduced Kroepoek Waroeng at a food expo in Dubai. Seeing international guests light up over Indonesian crackers gave us a mission: share our food heritage in a ready-to-munch, joyfully flavoured way.</p><p data-en="During the pandemic, we looked for locally made snacks our three-year-old would love—without the extras we did not want. We could not find enough, so we experimented with natural ingredients in our own kitchen. That is how our Fish &amp; Cheese series, and The Munching Queen, came to life." data-id="Saat pandemi, kami mencari camilan lokal yang disukai anak kami yang berusia tiga tahun—tanpa bahan tambahan yang tidak kami inginkan. Pilihannya belum cukup, jadi kami bereksperimen dengan bahan alami di dapur sendiri. Dari situlah seri Ikan &amp; Keju dan The Munching Queen lahir.">During the pandemic, we looked for locally made snacks our three-year-old would love—without the extras we did not want. We could not find enough, so we experimented with natural ingredients in our own kitchen. That is how our Fish & Cheese series, and The Munching Queen, came to life.</p><blockquote class="pullquote" data-en="We believe quality is key—and a better snack can taste every bit as good." data-id="Kami percaya kualitas adalah kunci—dan camilan yang lebih baik tetap bisa terasa sangat lezat.">We believe quality is key—and a better snack can taste every bit as good.</blockquote></div></div></section><section class="section tone-powder"><div class="container"><span class="eyebrow" data-en="A peek inside the pantry" data-id="Mengintip isi lemari camilan">A peek inside the pantry</span><h2 data-en="Something for every kind of munch." data-id="Ada camilan untuk setiap selera.">Something for every kind of munch.</h2><p class="lede muted" data-en="Savoury, sweet, familiar or adventurous—start with three family favourites." data-id="Gurih, manis, familiar, atau berani—mulai dari tiga favorit keluarga.">Savoury, sweet, familiar or adventurous—start with three family favourites.</p><div class="card-grid"><article class="product-card reveal"><div class="product-stage tone-butter"><img src="/images/products/fish-cheese/original.png" alt="Original snack package" width="900" height="900" loading="lazy"></div><div class="product-body"><div class="sizes"><span class="size">10g</span><span class="size">30g</span><span class="size">85g</span></div><h3 data-en="Original" data-id="Original">Original</h3><p data-en="The honest pairing of savoury fish and creamy cheese." data-id="Perpaduan jujur antara gurihnya ikan dan lembutnya keju.">The honest pairing of savoury fish and creamy cheese.</p><a class="button button--small" href="/contact" data-en="Find a store" data-id="Cari toko">Find a store</a></div></article><article class="product-card reveal"><div class="product-stage tone-blush"><img src="/images/products/brownies/chocolate.png" alt="Chocolate snack package" width="900" height="900" loading="lazy"></div><div class="product-body"><div class="sizes"><span class="size">35g</span></div><h3 data-en="Chocolate" data-id="Cokelat">Chocolate</h3><p data-en="Deep Belgian chocolate with a golden, delicate crunch." data-id="Cokelat Belgia yang kaya dengan kerenyahan tipis keemasan.">Deep Belgian chocolate with a golden, delicate crunch.</p><a class="button button--small" href="/contact" data-en="Find a store" data-id="Cari toko">Find a store</a></div></article><article class="product-card reveal"><div class="product-stage tone-mint"><img src="/images/products/tempeh/salmon-furikake.png" alt="Salmon Furikake snack package" width="900" height="900" loading="lazy"></div><div class="product-body"><div class="sizes"><span class="size">30g</span></div><h3 data-en="Salmon Furikake" data-id="Salmon Furikake">Salmon Furikake</h3><p data-en="Salmon, roasted seaweed, sesame and garlic in umami harmony." data-id="Salmon, rumput laut panggang, wijen, dan bawang putih yang penuh umami.">Salmon, roasted seaweed, sesame and garlic in umami harmony.</p><a class="button button--small" href="/contact" data-en="Find a store" data-id="Cari toko">Find a store</a></div></article></div><div class="button-row"><a class="button" href="/products" data-en="Explore all products" data-id="Lihat semua produk">Explore all products</a></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="center"><span class="eyebrow" data-en="Trust the process" data-id="Proses yang dapat dipercaya">Trust the process</span><h2 data-en="Made the right way, not the easy way." data-id="Dibuat dengan cara yang benar, bukan yang mudah.">Made the right way, not the easy way.</h2><p class="lede muted" data-en="Our facility, packaging and quality checks follow recognised food safety standards." data-id="Fasilitas, kemasan, dan pemeriksaan kualitas kami mengikuti standar keamanan pangan yang diakui.">Our facility, packaging and quality checks follow recognised food safety standards.</p></div><div class="cert-grid"><article class="cert-card reveal"><span class="cert-mark">ISO</span><h3>ISO 22000:2005</h3><p data-en="Certified food safety management facility." data-id="Fasilitas bersertifikat manajemen keamanan pangan.">Certified food safety management facility.</p></article><article class="cert-card reveal"><span class="cert-mark">H</span><h3>HACCP</h3><p data-en="Preventive control from biological, chemical, and physical hazards." data-id="Kendali preventif terhadap bahaya biologis, kimia, dan fisik.">Preventive control from biological, chemical, and physical hazards.</p></article><article class="cert-card reveal"><span class="cert-mark">BP</span><h3>BPOM</h3><p data-en="Products certified by Indonesia’s food and drug authority." data-id="Produk bersertifikat Badan Pengawas Obat dan Makanan.">Products certified by Indonesia’s food and drug authority.</p></article><article class="cert-card reveal"><span class="cert-mark">✓</span><h3>Halal</h3><p data-en="Halal certified for confident family snacking." data-id="Bersertifikat halal untuk camilan keluarga yang tepercaya.">Halal certified for confident family snacking.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="section section--tight"><div class="container"><div class="cta-panel reveal"><span class="eyebrow" data-en="Ready to munch?" data-id="Siap ngemil?">Ready to munch?</span><h2 data-en="Find your next favourite bag." data-id="Temukan kemasan favorit berikutnya.">Find your next favourite bag.</h2><div class="button-row" style="justify-content:center"><a class="button" href="/products" data-en="Browse flavours" data-id="Jelajahi rasa">Browse flavours</a><a class="button button--secondary" href="/contact" data-en="Where to buy" data-id="Tempat membeli">Where to buy</a></div></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="container"><span